Feature: Bus Ticket Booking on Abhibus

  Scenario: User books a bus ticket
    Given the user opens the Abhibus website
    When the user selects "Bangalore" as origin and "Goa" as destination
    And the user selects "Tomorrow" as the travel date
    And the user filters by "AC" and "Sleeper" bus types
    And the user selects seat "4UC"
    And the user selects the boarding and dropping points
    Then the user proceeds to payment
